title: Contracts and Injury Updates; Bunkercast Style News Rundown
itunes:title: Contracts and Injury Updates; Bunkercast Style News Rundown
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Colleen Wolfe bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including Trevor Lawrence named the starter and Travis Etienne being out for the season with an injury (7:28). Mac Jones has been outplaying Cam at practice (19:30) and Teddy Bridgewater is named the starter for the Broncos (22:41).
